{
  "stem": "22869.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Of course, it was all non-kosher, so nobody, at such a point, yet had in his wildest dreams that he would eat it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You were still having plenty, so to say, power in you to withstand such a outrageous-- didn't think to eat non-kosher food.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "At that time, they took us, and they loaded us in-- in a cattle train-- packed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, stuffed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, as the hours were going on, we began to realize that-- that these promises that we were given by our leadership at home and-- and by other-- other people, they probably had no knowledge of what's going on in this end of the world.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Otherwise, they probably would have warned us, you know, to escape in the first place.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they loaded us in the-- in these cattle trains.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we traveled-- I don't remember how many hours it took them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It couldn't have been too far, but it probably was between six and 12 hours when we landed in Lublin, in Poland.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The conditions on the trains were, I mean, were awful.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You realized that was, let's say, around Passover-- it was on Passover, 1942.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The weather wasn't very warm.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was early spring.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were squashed there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You had no way of sitting down.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was no way of standing up, either, because one guy was falling upon the other.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So the conditions were horrid.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And people had to go to the bathroom.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "If you had to go, you had to go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It's-- it's-- you know, you have to conform to your human needs.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So needless to say that it was-- it was-- it was awful.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I mean, you-- you began-- That was the-- the-- the beginning of the dehumanization of people.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
